headline.main: Pulse Nightclub Victims' Fund Will Make 2nd Payout
headline.print_headline: Pulse Nightclub Victims' Fund Will Make 2nd Payout

lead_paragraph: Survivors of the Pulse nightclub massacre and families of the victims will receive a second payout from the OneOrlando Fund.
